{"tid":812420,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有時覺得同朋友相處 仲辛苦過同另一半","createTime":"2018-09-09T15:28:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T17:14:25.000Z","uid":205823,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9888a60215a44745cdca6f7d3a8208cfc9fe84b0","tid":812420,"uid":205823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T15:28:35.000Z","msg":"閨蜜/死黨<br />\n有時鬧交 鬧到唔知以為係情侶就黎分手既節奏<br />\n但鬧完交 就好似情侶復合咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有冇人有同感</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"173345b90580e10c5d0807cbbe6675892339a834","tid":812420,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T15:31:28.000Z","msg":"女人嘅友誼好上淺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c1caca0f3228d2063335ff1eeeca82b6cdf6dea","tid":812420,"uid":198583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T15:31:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女人嘅友誼好膚淺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"8094906fc4a49281c1fb268653a210292fcf8b59","tid":812420,"uid":131622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T16:20:24.000Z","msg":"人緣唔好應該點改善？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e29de8e8e2dcd781614669dcaa47819cad637026","tid":812420,"uid":27793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T17:14:25.000Z","msg":"有試過<br />\n但無好返<br />\n因為大家價值觀太大分歧<br />\n即係同佢相處完會覺得好攰好攰<br />\n抽乾咁<br />\n<br />\n我身邊得返：就算長時間相處都會融洽同埋唔會覺得攰，相處落覺得舒服嘅好朋友"}]}